ure expansion detected.\n- Evidence includes required elements: changed files, executed commands, acceptance criteria, and explicit risks.\n- Boilerplate conventions appear preserved: AppShell/CompositionRoot wiring remains intact and coverage is additive (`CompositionRootTests`, `IntegrationWakeExploratoryUITests`).\n- No quality gate appears silently weakened or deferred; quality tools are required before report emission, with hosted macOS runner dependency documented.\n- Generated code remains testable and modular: checks are script-driven, UI integration test is isolated, and dependency composition remains factory-based and unit-test covered.\n- Independent re-verification on 2026-05-14 confirms the evidence remains accurate against current files and conventions.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
